Package: geojsonlint
Title: Lint 'GeoJSON'
Description: Tools for linting 'GeoJSON'. Includes tools for interacting with the
    online tool <http://geojsonlint.com>, and the Javascript library geojsonhint
    (<https://www.npmjs.com/package/geojsonhint>).
